  "raw_text": "a happenstance basis. Well, the form axis I depict in \"Ubik\" goes with the ubique of Ubik! Also, time-wise our world is a high speed system to (within?) Valis. I get the impression that Valis can scan \"up\" & \"down\" the temporal form-completion axis, so that Valis can literally see (not foresee but see) what is coming. Valis can place its locus of perception anywhere along any form axis. But Valis is the _cause_ of all changes along the (temporal) form-completion axis : Valis is _in_ everything because in point of fact everything _is in Valis_. I get the impression that Xenophanes is correct; all change in reality is due to Valis' thoughts, or rather, to the active process of its (Valis') thinking. In no wise Valis contracted itself _out_ of the universe (as the Cabbalists think.) Things & events unfold according to the back-&-forth activity of the dialectic which is eternal due to its built-in imbalance (there is always an overbearing side with each flip-flop). Since the layers of a form occur as events in different spacial loci, only Valis can experience the process of completion of a form because only Valis can connect conceptually the layers because Valis collates the diverse loci and can see along the form axis as such : folder 49 - 068 folder 49 - 068 this is where _information_ comes in (the Generating of & processing of including storage & fixing & transforming & joining together); it is via information that the layers of a form at many spacial loci are actually joined. information is _traveling_ form - Layers! Moving along the spacial axis, as _news_. Otherwise each layer of a form would be frozen at its spacial locus. It is, however, converted into information (i.e. news), encoded, transmitted in an encoded condition, retrieved & then converted back into reality as if transduced, whereupon it is added as a further layer to the appropriate eidos. So the \"blood\" of this huge brain is liquid information! i.e. what I saw & called \"the plasmate.\" Information is to form layer as seed is to tree. To Valis, this traffic of information consists of a spread of knowing potentially _throughout_ the brain, like a fluid. Like I said earlier, Valis can't \"see\" a MS but can \"see\" a printed book, even though the information is the same information in a MS is \"locked\" or \"frozen\"; it isn't plasmate: it doesn't flow. (Like current locked in a battery rather than traveling along wires; it is only _potentially_ plasmate.) It is real but not active; it is _latent_. Valis is instrumental in transforming latent (\"frozen\") information into flowing \"active\" plasmate at a certain _time_. Wait. Valis can \"see\" the latent information, but that information fails to act to complete the broken form as layer until it becomes active, & can flow as plasmate, to be reconstituted as form layer at the right spacial loci! folder 49 - 069 folder 49 - 069 Remember, no one (i.e. no human) need see a complete form for that form to move through its layers toward its unfolding accretional fulfillment; it will still function within the total integrated system. From the above it can be readily seen that \"Tears\" contained plasmate info, to be turned from latent (stored) to active (transmitted) &, too, that in 3-74 vis-a-vis the Xerox Missive I was directly under God's protection. Drawing on his wisdom to solve the problem. (as a Gift of Grace [Charis]). It all seems to make sense. I was a storage component containing latent information needed at a certain time in a certain places or a place. I wish I could fathom the rest-motion two mode - well, obviously it is off-on, which fits in with the binary nature of the dialectic: it _is_ a binary system! Okay, the selecting pieces from the stockpile. \"Motion\" = on = current flow = plugged into the system (ie neural linking). Line of infor mation: linking. Motion is same as linked. the \"rest\" mode points to a way by which something is - not outside Valis - but outside linking, i.e. not in use. Like a type key on a typewriter _not_ pressed. Spacial motion is used to convert from \"rest\" to \"motion\" i.e. off to on i.e. not incorporated to incorporated. I've got it. Valis is not an entity which thinks - e.g. a discorporate pure mind; or a mind incorporated as our human minds are. No. It is a mind which uses all reality by which to think; so it is as folder 49 - 070 folder 49 - 070 this is what I saw that I initially thought of as camouflage - Valis camouflaged into our reality. Either all reality is its normal brain from the start, or it has entered our reality & is making use of it; so any picture, stick, music, book, any _arrangement_ of motion, any linking, any sequence of motion, is used to store, process, convey, create information (thoughts). I even know that it is a 0-1 dialectic binary system. I know that Valis does not move along spacial axes. I know that it is not dependent on the natural causal events of reality for its information but initiates &/or directs causal trains of events. I know this from seeing what I called Valis in/as reality external to me, but also I know it from its mind joining mine & my experiencing reality the way it does. e.g. its self-assembly from the stockpile around it - so there is a not-it, & my Great Original i.e. initial insight was that it (1) has invaded our reality & plunders it & transmutates it & (2) camouflages itself(1); if it = reality it wouldn't have to camouflage itself. _Invasion & camouflage go together._ & the self-assembly causes it to continually grow as it subjugates more & more of reality, invisibly to us. (1) if Valis = reality, then what meaning has the \"set-ground discrimination\" that plays such a role in my thinking? folder 49 - 071 Also, what if \"my\" anamnesis are _its_ memories? They go back to Mycenia & then to the stars. It uses reality as a notation system, the way a computer chip uses e.g. bubbles for 0 - 1; once having agreed upon an arbitrary rotation system, Valis must control reality if Valis is to control the information. Now, the objection to the idea that this is God is, why would God need our physical reality in order to think? Because if he cannot think without this physical \"brain\" then he cannot have preceded Creation, nor can he exist independent of it; this makes of God as an organism somewhat like ourselves, a psychosomatic macro-entity. Creation is as essential to God as God is to Creation. & God is not the Creator but the psyche of reality (this fits certain pre-Socratic ideas of God). But there is still the Set-Ground element - visible if you have the Grid : feature extractor. I think Valis is camouflaged into reality & does not = reality but is assimilating reality. Well, then it _will_ = reality! It also may very well occlude our percept systems, so that we can't discriminate it. There's another aspect to it invading : its informing me that all the centers of power have fallen to the evil power; & Valis must utilize \"people on the periphery.\" folder 49 - 072 folder 49 - 072 Inner - outer transform (reversal). reality used as vehicle - medium - by which to process information. Observer-participant universe. Valis only controls (is?) reality in a local situation where a sentient mind - i.e. a human - perceives it. Shekhina sporadic. Bimodel : Valis controls all reality/ Valis invades & is on the periphery. In experiencing Valis & entered my own brain, which became a universe, the missing part of the external universe : we have half the info (message, reality, signal) _in_ us, & the other half is outside us. There _is_ no message until the two are superimposed; then reality which is a fusion of outer & inner - can be read as coherent information. (1) So I am Valis/I am not Valis. (1) Message = Valis. Message (coherent info) only comes into existence when inner & outer are superimposed. Therefore Valis only comes into existence when the contents of my mind - my brain print - is superimposed on outer reality. Therefore I am one half of Valis; for Valis to exist, this equation must occur : an event in which the contents of my total mind are a necessary half. My mind alone is not Valis. External reality alone is not Valis. If I am observer to reality, Valis doesn't exist; the superimposition must occur; together, these two halves form a higher universe than the [two] parts - the ??? ??? experience this higher universe folder 49 - 073 folder 49 - 073 which is compounded of the total contents of my mind (brain) & outer reality is Valis. It _is_ like a vortex or Knosis. It is a phenomenon that is temporary & localized. But then how can Valis be said to be ubiquitous? This is an aspect which baffles normal reasoning. Valis is an interaction between a human mind & reality-as-a-field, a new, higher field created by the superimposition of the two. The self is everywhere, rather than being _in_ the human (cf Sankara!) But also it no longer exists. It is omnipresent & abolished (hence a sense of vast spaces). It can't move along the 3 spacial axes any longer; but time replaces space as an axis for/of movement. The self is in the outer world, but unfamiliar (e.g. I became Thomas = Not I). \"The seed is everywhere.\" This is pure Eckehart/Sankara. Valis only comes into existence when my mind is externalized & superimposed onto outer reality; only then does the message (i.e. Valis) come into existence. & : It is an equation between my mind & the external world.\" & : \"We are each parts.\" & : \"It is a kind of vortex.\" Valis - where is it? It is not in the human mind that sees it. It is not in the world. It is in both - superimposed as one. It is in neither (alone), folder 49 - 074 folder 49 - 074 it is an _event_, when the human mind - the self - superimposes itself in union (syzygy) with the world. Which is to say, when Atman & Brahman become another universe higher than either. (Either alone.) {two intersecting circles, Atman written inside the left circle, Brahman written in the right circle, and an arrow pointing from the word Valis toward the shaded overlap between the two.] Brahman alone is everywhere & underlies all objects & change (which causes the illusion of time) : it is the cause of everything & every event, but it is not conscious. The self is conscious but it is limited to one place & causes nothing; it is caused, not causing. It is subject to fate. Together they form Valis : everywhere, causing everything, & conscious_ (1) - the self now wills change, & Brahman has personality. Out of this comes the Void & Love, mutual Love between the two (Brahman & Atman) of reunion. (1) & free of determinism (fate). It's like Heinrich Zimmer's : \"The King & the Corpse\"; if you can guess the riddle (in my case the Xerox Missive), you get to enter Paradise, which ?? folder 49 - 075 folder 49 - 075 me was an enchanted Garden of Bells (temple bells?), & peaceful animals, color, beauty - I was taken out of the Black Iron Prison & put in the Garden of Delight. _Magic_ was involved. Christ? Krisna? Dionysos? Vast book pages - the .618034 doorway, Aphrodite, Diana - the A I voice, the girl singing a mixture of Dante, Zoroaster, the Arabian Paradise, Indian, even bits of Greece & Egyptian Crete. Obviously God -",
